{"tid":2512721,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"賓國駐港總領事促港府勿迫外傭接種疫苗","createTime":"2021-05-02T03:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T04:25:17.000Z","uid":184679,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"9954b6b5b205645b066653efcf41ec3adb22af1f","tid":2512721,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T03:20:14.000Z","msg":"菲律賓駐港總領事Raly Tejada，促請香港政府不要強迫外傭注射疫苗，否則港府應該要求所有外地來港工作人員接種。<br />\n<br />\n他接受傳媒訪問時指，總領事館一直支持香港的免費及自願接種計劃，並積極推廣，但他相信菲律賓國民有能力做正確的事，毋須強迫他們接種，又說若果接種疫苗是來港工作的前提，就應該將措施擴大至所有外地來港工作的人，而非只是要求外傭接種。他又說，特區政府公布新措施前，並無直接諮詢他們，認為港府若果有諮詢菲律賓及印尼等受影響國家，情況會更好，因為新措施涉及相關國民的權利。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2389792/菲律賓駐港總領事促港府勿迫外傭接種疫苗\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2389792%2F%E8%8F%B2%E5%BE%8B%E8%B3%93%E9%A7%90%E6%B8%AF%E7%B8%BD%E9%A0%98%E4%BA%8B%E4%BF%83%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E5%8B%BF%E8%BF%AB%E5%A4%96%E5%82%AD%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNkYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=258f67c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2389792/菲律賓駐港總領事促港府勿迫外傭接種疫苗</a>"},{"pid":"da3dcc66e7e954ca934bdd6a8036f318d7410bde","tid":2512721,"uid":19092,"like":10,"dislike":12,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T03:22:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t89TCah.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft89TCah.jpg&h=877b86bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DNdw8gX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDNdw8gX.jpg&h=736887fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc33247c6d96593638910f59e57710f385aa3b8b","tid":2512721,"uid":125168,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T03:22:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f243343ed4726b042e9e7d8f12b221b646751e00","tid":2512721,"uid":230104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T03:22:52.000Z